duties_responsibilities.duty: Provides front office support to clinical operations, including patient intake, registration, payments, and scheduling.
Answers phone calls and provides assistance to inquiries with good interpersonal skills.
Works under the daily supervision of the Practice Site Manager and/or assigned staff.
Maintains effective working relationship with other employees.
Lifts 25 pounds, occasional kneeling, pushing/pulling, and reaching.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or equivalent required
